<h2>About v2.1.5 Update</h2>
<ul>
<li>✨ New Features

<ul>
<li>Added a feature to show system uptime.</li>
<li>Added a feature to show awake time.</li>
<li>Added <code>Auto compact mode</code>, which automatically switches to compact mode when there is only one display.</li>
</ul></li>
<li>⚡️ Improvements

<ul>
<li>Added the ability to specify the font size for seconds in the time display.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p>
